content: On an adjusted basis for the third quarter, Delek U.S. had net income of $1.1 million or $0.02 per share compared to a net income of $3.6 million or $0.05 per share in prior year period. Maybe just as we look forward to 2023, you're spending $300 million in CapEx -- this year in 2022. I think $300 million this year, obviously, a lot of that was dependent on growth that we've seen in gathering and across the system.
